"""
AWP Baker - Workspace Color Manager
Generate GTK + Icon + Cursor themes and update workspace colors in INI.

Features:
- Read workspaces from AWP config
- Select which preset to work with
- Pick a color for a specific workspace
- Update INI with new color and theme names
- Bake themes with new color
- Copy icon to preset folder
- Recreate symlinks via awp_start.sh (only for current preset)
- Fool Bake: Pure theme baking without workspace operations
- Regenerate All: Rebuild ALL themes from INI
- Clean Start: Remove old themes before regenerating
- Smart checkbox interactions: Fool Bake disables everything, Clean auto-enables Regenerate

Usage:
    python3 awp_baker.py
"""

